  "text": "In Section 2, we summarize the modeling framework in [CITATION_1] . In Section 3, we introduce the Bayesian model and inference. In Section 4, we discuss the subject-specific predictions and evaluations using our modeling framework. A simulation study is used in Section 5 to illustrate the methodology. The proposed methods are applied in Section 6 to the ATBC study dataset. Finally, the article is concluded with a discussion in Section 7.",
